// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DdKBDh asymmetric blocks layers tower, 2023 by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/Dd3BDs asymmetric blocks dda plugin

// Tower formed of layers of asymmetric blocks
// with a symmetric core with space for staircase.

// Related:
// The basic pattern
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dstfzf asymmetric blocks compactified float
// Regularity/symmetry control
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mdyfD1 asymmetric blocks with regular spot
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/msGBD1  asymmetric blocks morph to grid
// Renderer
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dd3fDj raymarch voxels
// modified for asymmetric blocks instead of plain voxels
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/Dd3BDs asymmetric blocks dda plugin
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dscfDl asymmetric blocks bounce spheres

// Thanks to Shane for suggesting the DDA-plugin / snap-to-voxel method & for describing the asymmetric blocks!

// tags: 3d, random, tower, t, dda, blocks, portal, double, layer, regular, building, alternating, irregular, asymmetric, symmetric

